In a message dated 6/4/03 12:40:43 AM Central Daylight Time, 
foxmanroar1@... writes:


> Scourge's evil laughter burst through the air. "I am not the commander of 
> the ark?" Maxima my dear, you should scurry back to hydras, other then that 
> your all on dangerous ground, the grounds around here now belong to the 
> teracons, leave now or prepare for battle." 
> 

She didn't go far & hovered above Kup & the Bots. "Scourge... you are far too 
overconfident." She glared, tired & not in the mood to be dealing with this. 
She would leave this all to Rodimus & her talk with him. 

With that she turned & started back to Pred Base.

--part1_5b.39c3cd04.2c0ee10a_boundary
